{
  "texts": [
    "The human-written tweets were randomly sampled from the human-written data collection described in Sec. 3.1.",
    "The AI-generated tweets were also randomly sampled from the sets of tweets generated by the base or fine-tuned (on the 'large' 2,000 sample) GPT-4o models, respectively, for the same five topics using the Topic prompt.",
    "The fine-tuned model generated a small percentage of tweets (0.64%) in a language other than English; those tweets were not included in the human study.",
    "Participants were asked to select one of the two labels, 'human-written' or 'AI-generated', as the most likely source for each tweet.",
    "They could also optionally indicate in a free-form textbox which cues they relied upon when doing the task."
  ]
}